essional":"专业表达","Sound casual":"非正式表达","Sound concise":"简洁表达","Sound engaging":"有吸引力的表达","Sound enthusiastic":"热情的表达","Sound confident":"自信的表达","Translate":"翻译","English":"英语","French":"法语","German":"德语","Spanish":"西班牙语","Japanese":"日语","Hebrew":"希伯来语","Korean":"韩语","Chinese":"中文","Portuguese":"葡萄牙语","Vietnamese":"越南语","Greek":"希腊语","Polish":"波兰语","Change format":"更改格式","Elaborate":"详尽阐述","Shorten":"缩短","Retry":"重试","Auto Length":"自动长度","Shorter":"短","Longer":"已详尽阐述","AI analyzes the user input to set the length":"AI 分析用户输入以设置长度","Icons":"图标","Settings":"设置","Next":"下一步","Ok, got it":"好的，知道了","Done":"完成","Introducing the AI Action Bar":"AI 操作栏简介","Discover the power of your AI copilot to get the next best actions in the flow of your work.":"探索您的 AI 助手的强大功能，以便在工作流程中采取下一步最佳行动。","Upgraded Menu":"升级的菜单","Open the menu to get instant answers to your questions with our conversational AI Chat":"打开菜单，通过我们的对话式 AI 聊天即时获得问题的答案","Draft content from scratch with the help of AI":"借助 AI，从头开始起草内容","Highlighted text tools":"高亮文本工具","Highlight text to use AI reading and writing tools, including text summarization, translation, and writing editing tools.":"高亮显示文本，以使用 AI 阅读和写作工具，包括文本汇总、翻译和写作编辑工具。","Create your own actions":"创建您自己的操作","Create and save your own personalized prompts for fast reuse whenever text is highlighted on screen.":"创建并保存您自己的个性化提示，以便在屏幕上高亮显示文本时快速重复使用。","Workflow tools":"工作流程工具","Get workflow suggestions from your organization in the right place at the right time.":"在合适的时间、合适的位置从您的组织获取工作流程建议。","Text tools":"文本工具","More actions":"更多操作","Create new action":"新建操作","Edit highlighted text with AI":"使用 AI 编辑高亮文本","Create and save your own custom prompts":"创建并保存您自己的自定义提示","My actions":"我的操作","System actions":"系统操作","Contextual Action Bar":"上下文操作栏","More Settings":"更多设置","Text Tools Display":"文本工具显示","Some actions, made by your organization will still appear in the action bar":"您的组织执行的一些操作仍将显示在操作栏中","Hide always":"始终隐藏","Hide on this site":"在此网站上隐藏","Learn more":"了解详情","My custom actions":"我的自定义操作","My actions:":"我的操作：","All apps":"所有应用","Location-specific":"特定位置","Replay onboarding guide":"重播入门指南","Smart highlights":"智能亮点","Get instant details on people and customers by hovering over highlighted names":"将鼠标悬停在突出显示的名字上，即可获得有关人员和客户的即时详细信息","Tone":"语气","Format":"格式","Length":"长度","Language":"语言","Suggestions":"建议","Tools":"工具","Add custom action":"添加自定义操作","Stop listening":"停止聆听","Use microphone":"使用麦克风","I\'m listening...":"我在听…","Microphone disabled. Please enable it to be heard":"麦克风已禁用。 请将其启用，以便听到您的声音","Please enable mic to be heard":"请启用麦克风，以便听到您的声音","Hide from bar":"从操作栏中隐藏","Add to bar":"添加到操作栏","Delete":"删除","Refresh":"刷新","Rephrase":"复述","No more space in your bar":"您的操作栏没有额外空间","No actions available":"没有可用的操作","Got It":"知道了","Don’t show again":"不再显示","We noticed you use this action often":"我们注意到您经常使用此操作","To quickly reuse, right-click the action and add to the bar. Undo anytime.":"要快速重复使用，请右键单击此操作并将其添加到操作栏中。 可以随时撤消。","Find your custom action here":"在此处查找您的自定义操作","Right-click the action to edit, delete, or hide from the bar.":"右键单击此操作，可编辑、删除或从操作栏中隐藏。","You can find your hidden action here.":"您可以在这里找到您的隐藏操作。","Right click and select ‘Hide from bar’ to undo":"右键单击并选择“从操作栏中隐藏”，即可撤销","Right-click the action to edit or delete.":"右键单击要编辑或删除的操作。","Approaching the character limit":"即将达到字符上限","Character limit reached":"已达到字符上限","Add to memory":"添加到记忆中","Add Memory":"添加记忆","Add selected text to memory":"将选定文本添加到记忆中","An error occurred":"发生错误","Failed to generate memories":"无法生成记忆","Scanning this page for memory suggestions...":"正在扫描此页面以获取记忆建议…","Share anything you’d like us to remember to improve future AI responses.":"分享您希望我们记住的任何内容，以改进未来的 AI 响应。","Type your own memory...":"键入您自己的记忆…","Saved to memory!":"已保存到记忆中！","Manage information in the AI\'s memory to improve future responses.":"管理 AI 记忆中的信息，以改进未来的响应。","Manage Memory":"管理记忆","Memory":"记忆","Memories":"记忆","Search...":"搜索…","Add new memory...":"新增记忆…","Add":"添加","Edit memory":"编辑记忆","Delete memory":"删除记忆","Clear all memories":"清除所有记忆","No memories added yet":"尚未添加任何记忆","Saved memory":"保存的记忆","Saved in":"已保存于","Created date":"创建日期","Updated date":"更新日期","Manage memories":"管理记忆","Generate in chat":"在聊天中生成","Sort":"排序","Sorted up":"已按升序排列","Sorted down":"已按降序排列","Memory updated successfully":"记忆更新成功","This will permanently remove all saved memories, and the AI will no longer use it to improve future responses.":"此操作将永久移除保存的所有记忆，并且 AI 不会再用它来改进未来的响应。","Right-Click any action":"右键单击任何操作","to explore additional options such as hiding it from the bar, adding it into the bar, and making edits.":"探索其他选项，例如，将其从操作栏中隐藏、将其添加到操作栏中，以及进行编辑。","Proactive memory suggestion":"主动记忆建议","Enable to receive memory suggestion action when the page contains relevant information":"启用后，可在页面包含相关信息时接收记忆建议操作","Relevant Memory":"相关记忆","Enabling this will disable the Hide on this site toggle.":"启用此选项后，将禁用“在此网站上隐藏”开关。","Generating response...":"正在生成响应…","Chat response:":"聊天响应：","Personalization":"个性化","Customization":"定制","Get better responses by sharing who you are and how you work":"通过分享您的身份和工作方式，获得更好的响应","Introduce yourself to get better, more personalized responses":"介绍您自己，以获得更好、更加个性化的响应","How would you like to be called?":"您希望别人怎么称呼您？","Your name":"您的姓名","What do you do?":"您是做什么工作的？","Sales agent at Acme":"Acme 的销售代理","How would you like the AI to respond?":"您希望 AI 如何响应？","Custom":"自定义","Straight Shooter":"直言不讳","Collaborator":"协作者","Task Master":"任务管理者","Decision Advisor":"决策顾问","Type your communication preferences...":"键入您的沟通偏好...","Restore":"恢复","Anything else the AI should know about you?":"您还有希望 AI 知道的其他事情吗？","Job responsibilities, areas of interest, career goals":"工作职责、兴趣领域、职业目标","Generating a prompt that matches your role...":"正在生成与您的角色匹配的提示...","Enable personalization":"启用个性化设置","Run a quick action":"运行快速操作","Hey":"嘿","Ask me anything...":"问我任何问题...","Ask me anything about this page...":"询问我有关此页面的任何问题...","Ask me anything about the text you highlighted...":"询问我有关高亮文本的任何问题...","Ask me anything about what you typed in the field...":"询问我与您在字段中键入的内容相关的任何问题…","Use":"使用","Ignore":"忽略","New webpage identified":"发现新网页","New highlighted text identified":"发现新的高亮文本","Webpage identified":"发现网页","Highlighted text identified":"发现高亮文本","Text field identified":"发现文本字段","New text field identified":"发现新的文本字段","Would you prefer to use this as context for the AI, rather than the webpage?":"您是否更喜欢将其用作 AI 的上下文，而非网页？","Would you prefer to use this as context for the AI, rather than the previous webpage?":"您是否更喜欢将其用作 AI 的上下文，而非上一个网页？","Would you prefer to use this as context for the AI, rather than the text you highlighted earlier?":"您是否更喜欢将其用作 AI 的上下文，而非之前的高亮文本？","Would you prefer to use this as context for the AI, rather than the text in the previous field?":"您是否更喜欢将其用作 AI 的上下文，而非上一个字段中的文本？","Would you like to use this as context for the AI?":"您是否希望将其用作 AI 的上下文？","The AI can tailor its responses based on context like text you highlight, the page you\'re on, or text you type in a field":"AI 可以根据上下文（例如高亮文本、您所处的页面或您在字段中键入的文本）定制响应","Webpage":"网页","Highlighted text":"高亮文本","Text field":"文本字段","Add context":"添加上下文","Choose this to focus the AI response on a specific part of the page.":"选择此选项，可使 AI 响应专注于页面的特定部分。","To use, highlight text on screen first.":"要使用此功能，请先在屏幕上高亮显示文本。","Choose this to focus the AI response on text you\'ve typed in a specific field.":"选择此选项，可使 AI 响应专注于您在特定字段中键入的文本。","To use, click a text field that already contains text.":"要使用此功能，请单击已包含文本的文本字段。","Notifications":"通知","More notifications":"更多通知","Clear":"清除","Clear all":"全部清除","Pin to screen":"固定到屏幕","Hide for 1 Hour":"隐藏 1 小时","Hide options":"隐藏选项","Restart":"重启","Run automation":"运行自动化","Ask me to do any task for you":"让我为您执行任何任务","Creating a draft...":"正在创建草稿…","AI Chats":"AI 聊天","Help Content":"帮助内容","WalkMe Menu":"WalkMe 菜单","Learning Content":"学习内容","Open sidebar":"打开侧边栏","Set as default":"设为默认值","The AI will use the information you provide to tailor it\'s responses to you.":"AI 将利用您提供的信息来定制对您的响应。","Learn more about how we use your data":"详细了解我们如何使用您的数据","You can tell the AI to do things like:\\n* Be opinionated. If a question could have multiple answers, try to give only the best one\\n* Be casual and friendly\\n* Be concise and professional":"您可以让 AI 执行以下操作：\\n* 大胆表达观点。 如果一个问题可能有多个答案，请尝试仅给出最佳答案\\n* 随意且友好\\n* 简洁且专业","Delivering only blunt facts or instructions—no filler, no questions, no fluff.":"仅提供直接的事实或说明，没有填充词、没有问句、没有废话。","Brainstorming support with friendly tone, multiple perspectives, and open-ended prompts.":"用友好的语气、多个视角和开放式提示提供头脑风暴支持。","Breaking tasks into concise checklists and focusing on fast, action-oriented execution.":"将任务分解成简洁的检查表，专注于以行动为导向的快速执行。","Framing choices with data-driven pros/cons and clear, strategic recommendations.":"用数据驱动的优缺点和清晰的战略建议来构建选择框架。","Sources":"来源","Personal AI memory":"个人 AI 记忆","Improve my prompt":"改进我的提示","Undo":"撤销","Redo":"重做","Improving your prompt...":"正在改进您的提示…","Meet the Action Bar":"认识操作栏","A secure, company-provided AI tool to improve your daily work.":"公司提供的安全 AI 工具，可改进您的日常工作。","What is your role?":"您的角色是什么？","Share a little about yourself so the Action Bar can personalize your experience.":"分享一些关于您的信息，让操作栏为您提供个性化的体验。","Example: Sales manager at Acme":"示例：Acme 销售经理","Continue without role":"不选择角色并继续","Continue":"继续","Chat with AI or explore resources":"与 AI 聊天或探索资源","Chat with AI for guidance or explore curated company resources to get the help you need.":"与 AI 聊天以获取指导，或探索精选公司资源以获得所需帮助。","Chat with AI":"与 AI 聊天","Chat with AI to ask questions and complete your daily tasks faster.":"与 AI 聊天，提出问题，更快地完成日常任务。","Find helpful resources":"查找有用的资源","Explore curated company resources and app-specific tips to guide your work.":"探索精选公司资源和应用专属提示，为您的工作提供指导。","Get quick help":"快速获取帮助","Ask your question":"提出您的问题","Action Bar understands what you’re working on":"操作栏理解您正在处理的任务","Ask AI about this page":"向 AI 询问此页面的情况","The Action Bar understands what you’re working on and uses that to run quick actions, like editing text, answering questions, or scanning for key details.":"操作栏理解您正在处理的任务，并用它来运行快速操作，如编辑文本、回答问题或搜索关键详细信息。","Use ready-made AI tools":"使用现成 AI 工具","Run instant actions like Summarize, Proofread, or Translate, all designed to work with what’s on your screen and give you instant, relevant results.":"运行即时操作，如总结、校对或翻译，这些操作都可与屏幕上的任务协同运行，并为您提供即时且相关的结果。","Create and save your own actions":"创建并保存您自己的操作","Not seeing actions or recommendations you need? Turn your favorite prompts into reusable AI actions going forward.":"没有看到您需要的操作或建议？将您最喜欢的提示转换为以后可重用的 AI 操作。","Turn this into a LinkedIn post":"将其转换为 LinkedIn 帖子","Draft a response message":"编写响应消息","Find next steps":"查找后续操作","Personalize the Action Bar":"操作栏个性化","Set the tone, style, display settings, and more to match how you like to work. Once set, the Action Bar will use these preferences automatically.":"根据您喜欢的工作方式，设置色调、样式、显示设置等。设置后，操作栏将自动使用这些偏好设置。","I am a sales agent at Acme corp.":"我是 Acme 公司的销售代理。","I prefer concise answers":"我喜欢简洁的答案","Your privacy comes first":"您的隐私排在第一位","Your information is processed securely and is never used to train the AI models.":"您的信息会得到安全处理，永远不会用于训练 AI 模型。","You stay in control":"您的信息尽在您的掌控之中","No data training on your content":"我们未使用您的内容进行数据训练","Data processed within your company":"数据均在您公司内部处理","Saved to memory":"已保存到记忆中","Save key information to Memory":"将关键信息保存到记忆中","Save key details for later, so the Action Bar can provide more relevant recommendations and support. You control what\'s stored at all times.":"保存关键详细信息以供以后使用，以便操作栏提供更相关的建议和支持。存储的内容始终由您掌控。","Customize your Action Bar":"自定义操作栏","Right-click any action to hide tools you don’t need, pin the ones you use most, or edit custom actions to fit how you work.":"右键单击任何操作，以根据您的工作方式隐藏不需要的工具，固定最常用的工具，或编辑自定义操作。","Manage what the Action Bar remembers":"管理操作栏记住的信息","Review, edit, delete, or add memories to keep the Action Bar’s saved information accurate and relevant to your work.":"查看、编辑、删除或添加记忆，使操作栏中保存的信息始终准确且与您的工作相关。","Get smart workflow suggestions":"获取智能工作流建议","These actions are provided by your organization and are condition-based, appearing automatically when relevant to your page or task.":"这些操作由您的组织提供，并且基于条件，在与您的页面或任务相关时自动显示。","Start tour":"开始导览","Skip tour":"跳过导览","AI Chat":"AI 聊天","Resources":"资源","Reading Tools":"阅读工具","Summarize":"总结","Writing Tools":"写作工具","Change Tone":"更改语气","Improve":"改进","Secure processing":"安全处理","Account renewal due Dec 10":"帐户续订截止日期为12月10日","Finance lead: Sarah Kim":"财务负责人: Sarah Kim","Save key details for smarter recommendations. Managed by you.":"保存关键详细信息以获得更明智的建议。 由您管理。","AI Action":"AI 操作","Right-click an action to pin, hide, or edit your workspace.":"右键单击操作以固定、隐藏或编辑您的工作空间。","I am a sales agent":"我是销售代理","Set your role and communication preferences to match how you like to work.":"设置您的角色和沟通偏好，以符合您的工作方式。","Keep saved information accurate and relevant to your work.":"确保保存的信息准确且与您的工作相关。","Turn this into a post":"将其转换为帖子","Draft a message":"起草消息","Save your go-to prompts":"保存您的导航提示","Not seeing what you need? Turn your favorite prompts into reusable AI actions.":"没有找到您需要的内容？ 将您最喜欢的提示转换为可重复使用的 AI 操作。","Ask your question...":"提出您的问题...","Action Bar understands context":"操作栏理解上下文","The Action Bar uses your page to answer questions, scan for key details or edit text.":"操作栏使用您的页面来回答问题、扫描关键详细信息或编辑文本。","Designed to work with what\'s on your screen and give you instant, relevant results.":"该软件旨在与屏幕上的内容配合使用，并为您提供即时的相关结果。","Provided by your organization and appear when relevant to your page or task.":"由您的组织提供，在与您的页面或任务相关时显示。","Unhide Action Bar":"显示操作栏","Tools group":"工具组","Automatically expand":"自动展开","Hide action bar":"隐藏操作栏","Hide for 1 hour":"隐藏1小时","Hide everywhere":"在所有地方隐藏","Disabled while \'Hide for 1 hour\' is active":"\'隐藏1小时\'激活时禁用","Disabled while \'Hide everywhere\' is active":"\'在所有地方隐藏\'激活时禁用","Help menu":"帮助菜单"}')}}]);